## ⚠️ Prerequisites

You need **valid API keys** for LLM providers:

| Provider | Link |
|----------|------|
| OpenAI | [API Keys](https://platform.openai.com/api-keys) |
| Cohere | [API Keys](https://dashboard.cohere.com/api-keys) |
| Hugging Face | [Access Tokens](https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens) |

> ⚠️ The app won’t function without at least one valid API key.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 🧠 Core AI Features

- Upload **PDF/DOCX** documents  
- Automatic **text extraction & chunking**  
- Embeddings generation (`all-MiniLM-L6-v2`)  
- Semantic search via **FAISS vector database**  
- Context-aware **Q&A with RAG**

### 🤖 Multi-LLM Support

- OpenAI, Cohere, Hugging Face  
- Dynamic **top-5 relevant models discovery**  
- Real-time **token streaming**  
- Provider badges & dynamic model indicators  

### 💬 User Experience

- Chat-style interface (ChatGPT-like)  
- Streaming responses with cursor effect  
- Source document references  
- Persistent vector index (no reprocessing needed)  

---

## 🏗 Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD;
    User --> UI[Streamlit Dashboard]
    UI --> QASystem
    QASystem --> Retriever[FAISS Retriever]
    Retriever --> RelevantChunks[Relevant Document Chunks]
    RelevantChunks --> LLM[LLM (OpenAI/Cohere/HF)]
    LLM --> Streaming[Streaming Response]
    Streaming --> UI
````

**Workflow:** Upload documents → Chunk & embed → Query → Retrieve → Stream response.

